and auto-encoders (Wu et al., 2016b; Liang et al., 2018a)) can be used as the
translation function. Given user and item embeddings, the two-tower model
makes a prediction for each user-item pair. Cosine similarity and inner product
are usually adopted to measure the embedding distance, so we have:
