responses of users to advertisements of inventory in the user profile and
advertising information. The time length of the data is eight days, and the
dataset is divided into four tables: advertisement features, user profiles, past
shopping behavior that users engaged in, and who received the advertisement
with responses.1
• Instacart.MB dataset (Sheng et al., 2021): The Instacart Market Basket
