Model input/output.
The input to the model
is a sequence comprised of the query or the
natural language question, followed by a se-
quence of input tables, represented by the ta-
ble name and the corresponding flattened ta-
ble. Table names are important for disambiguat-
ing tables in multi-table QA setting.
Specif-
