question [table1 rep] [table2 rep] . . . [tablen rep]
where [tablei rep] is the representation of the i-th
table. As depicted in Figure 2, the i-th table is
flattened in row-major format and represented as
<table_name>: n1 n2 | col: h1 | h2 | . . . | hk
