Many pre-trained ranking models do not output the uncertainty
scores 𝜎𝑞,𝑖that PUFR employs to reorder rankings. Thus we need a
way to approximate the uncertainty scores 𝜎𝑞,𝑖in a post-processing
manner. Next, we show how to do this with the help of Laplace
approximation.
