the concatenation of learnable item embeddings and associated
clicks over the whole slate, and outputs (𝜇𝜙(𝑎,𝑐), log 𝜎𝜙(𝑎,𝑐)). For
the decoder 𝑝𝜃(𝑎,𝑐|𝑧), another MLP takes as input the latent sam-
